                    <span>This book is well written but I was expected something more advanced. If you have been a real J2EE developer for at least a year, you would probably have run across some if not most of the problems already. You also would have worked around them using solutions from other Java books you have.<P>This is a good book for new developers. They should be able to recognize problems early on after reading this book.</span>
                  
